com.karusmc.commons.commands

Class CommandMapProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.karusmc.commons.commands.CommandMapProxy

  • public class CommandMapProxy
extends Object
    Acts as a proxy for the server's internal CommandMap implementation. This class does not replace the server's internal CommandMap implementation. Allows plug-ins to listen for CommandRegistrationEvent registered via this class. CommandRegistrationEvent will be called only when commands are registered through this class and not if directly through the underlying CommandMap implementation.
